dc_title_s: South America, Golfo de Morrosquillo and approaches (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by soundings and isolines. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "From a Colombian chart of 1996 and U.S. Navy surveys to 1938." "Copyright 1997 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram. Map no.24512. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA). United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency. (1997). South America, Golfo de Morrosquillo and approaches (Raster Image). LandInfo. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/xj987jy7411 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
